{"talk":{"id":54750,"name":"Kelsey Leonard: Why lakes and rivers should have the same rights as humans","description":"Water is essential to life. Yet in the eyes of the law, it remains largely unprotected -- leaving many communities without access to safe drinking water, says legal scholar Kelsey Leonard. In this powerful talk, she shows why granting lakes and rivers legal \"personhood\" -- giving them the same legal rights as humans -- is the first step to protecting our bodies of water and fundamentally transforming how we value this vital resource.","slug":"kelsey_leonard_why_lakes_and_rivers_should_have_the_same_rights_as_humans","recorded_at":"2019-12-04 00:00:00","published_at":"2019-12-13 15:58:24","updated_at":"2021-02-10 22:28:03","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":618,"name":"TEDWomen 2019"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/e32fa8b924d8aa0326ad3150428ae6cf97f154ab_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/e32fa8b924d8aa0326ad3150428ae6cf97f154ab_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/e32fa8b924d8aa0326ad3150428ae6cf97f154ab_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/e32fa8b924d8aa0326ad3150428ae6cf97f154ab_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2f60a914f19b0cd8118911e1e23f344ef44b5b28_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/KelseyLeonard_2019W-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6608560,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/KelseyLeonard_2019W-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":18297952,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/KelseyLeonard_2019W-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":32401038,"mime_t